fields.description: This assignment covers Degree of Polynomials, Coeffiecients of Polynomials and Classification of Polynomials as Cubic, Quadratic and Polynomials in two or three variables.
This assignment covers Zeroes of a Polynomials and Division of two Polynomials by Long Division Method.
This assignment covers Remainder theorem, Factor Theorem and Factorisation of Polynomials.
This assignment covers Expansion and Factorisation of Polynomials and Numbers using Algebraic Identities.
This assignment covers Basics of Number Systems, Rational Numbers, Irrational Numbers and Location of Numbers on a Number Line.
This assignment covers Real Numbers and their Decimal Expansion, Expressing Numbers in the form of \(\frac{p}{q}\) and Listing Irrational Numbers between any two numbers.
This assignment covers Mathematical Operations on Rational and Irrational Numbers and Representing Square Roots of Decimal numbers on the number line.
This assignment covers Simplification of Expressions using identites, Rationalization of Denominator and Laws of Exponents for Real Numbers.
This assignment covers surface area of cuboids and cubes.
This assignment covers curved surface area and total surface area of cylinders.
This assignment covers curved surface area and total surface area of cones.
This assignment covers surface area of spheres and curved surface area and total surface area of hemispheres.
This assignment covers volume of cuboids and cubes.
This assignment covers volume of cylinders.
This assignment covers volume of cones.
This assignment covers volume of spheres and hemispheres.
